show.description: DEA agents respond to a beach crime scene and find a missing college girl on a drug-runners' boat. As she recounts her spring break trip turned nightmare, the investigation delves into drugs, betrayal, and murder. Pursuing smugglers and missing teens, the agents uncover the dark legend of Immortal Island.
